CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 15, 1939, pg. 7, reads: "Wednesday Bridge Club Hostesses to Beautiful Holiday Event at Loendi - Scenes at the Wednesday Bridge Club's Easter Monday party at Loendi... Second row, left: Mrs. Ella Powell, Mrs. Mae Harris, Mrs. Ethel Grant, Mrs. Bertie West. in background: Mrs. Ethel Adams, Mrs. Emmett Davis, Mrs. Carolyn Williams... Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Women, including Ella Powell, Mae Harris, Ethel Grant, Bertie West, Ethel Adams, Emmett Davis, and Carolyn Williams, playing bridge card game in Loendi Club
